.mod-rtl.value: linear-gradient( to right, transparent var(--size-4-6), black var(--size-4-6) )

.checkbox-container.value: box-shadow 0.15s ease-in-out, outline 0.15s ease-in-out, border 0.15s ease-in-out, opacity 0.15s ease-in-out

.checkbox-container:after.value: transform 0.15s ease-in-out, width 0.1s ease-in-out, left 0.1s ease-in-out

.theme-dark .pdf-container.mod-themed .p.value: drop-shadow(0px 0px 1px var(--color-base-60)) drop-shadow(0px 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4)) drop-shadow(0px 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4))

.popupWrapper > div.value: drop-shadow(0px 0px 1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2)) drop-shadow(0px 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3)) drop-shadow(0px 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3))

.canvas-color-picker-item.canvas-color-p.value: conic-gradient( var(--color-red), var(--color-yellow), var(--color-green), var(--color-blue), var(--color-purple), var(--color-red) )

.mobile-navbar-text.value: linear-gradient( to left, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) var(--size-4-4), #000000 var(--size-4-8) )

body.doc-title-accent .inline-title.value: linear-gradient( var(--gradientDegree), hsl(calc(var(--accent-h) + 30), var(--primary-sat), var(--primary-lit)) 0, hsl(calc(var(--accent-h) - 30), var(--primary-sat), var(--primary-lit)) 100% )

body.doc-title-rainbow .inline-title.value: linear-gradient( var(--gradientDegree), var(--pink) 0, var(--orange) 8.33%, var(--yellow) 16.66%, var(--green) 25%, var(--blue) 33.33%, var(--purple) 41.66%, var(--pink) 50%, var(--orange) 58.33%, var(--yellow) 66.66%, var(--green) 75%, var(--blue) 83.33%, var(--purple) 91.66%, var(--pink) 100% )

filter.dark: drop-shadow(0px 0px 1px var(--color-base-60)) drop-shadow(0px 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4)) drop-shadow(0px 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4))
